name: Cowboy Love is Pure 1-012: I Will Pay Attention To Girls
description: Chapter 1, panel 12. A cowboy may proclaim beneath his god and his sky and a centipede that matters of love and girls are to be paramount to his heart and mind going forward. The centipede's words hang above them like dark clouds. Thunder rumbles from beneath the ground. A comic by Little Old Man. This panel is an edition of 30.
